{"tid":666354,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，男朋友逼我一定要去船P…","createTime":"2018-05-15T20:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T04:18:28.000Z","uid":5770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"422241fdb5317847d1b3801f435bf3cfe69bc25f","tid":666354,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T20:46:35.000Z","msg":"因為男朋友講左好多次叫我同佢班朋友出去，但我一直好自卑唔敢見佢D朋友，男朋友琴日話今次船P無得我唔去，因為佢所有朋友都帶左自己男/女朋友去，佢唔想得佢一個人咁去，佢語氣重到好似我唔去既話，就會同我分手...<br />\n<br />\n但我平時飯聚都唔敢去，仲點敢去呢D要著泳衣既場合呀，我見佢D女仔朋友個個又瘦又白滑，而我仲係肥肥地又未脫毛，如果游水既時候露左D毛出黎咪仲失禮，咁不如直接唔好去啦...有咩方法可以勸掂男朋友唔帶我去??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c254391e671e20570137a60a97503d17c60b8e4f","tid":666354,"uid":183149,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T20:57:58.000Z","msg":"船p前一日或者個日朝早剃晒佢咪得<br />\n泳衣外面加多件薄薄地透透地既衫 再加條沙灘褲<br />\n咁咪攪掂"},{"pid":"08b1fa369350e208ffbaae77204ca29b25e2d988","tid":666354,"uid":44038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T20:59:02.000Z","msg":"脫毛好簡單姐, 如果唔想露咪著件薄浴袍係外面"},{"pid":"8d8425be9a72523f7f2523ea8820c4c8f3b1bf2d","tid":666354,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T20:59:28.000Z","msg":"係咪公海?"},{"pid":"ea8c941357ee48bd7e0f9f1d816739225cb2389d","tid":666354,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T21:31:23.000Z","msg":"女仔朋友圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e24b65ddd79a11b448fe84917febdafcd12f7bf","tid":666354,"uid":23433,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T21:33:44.000Z","msg":"去囉<br />\n多個人夾多份錢<br />\n搞手都係想求個和姐"},{"pid":"ca3b476d4283cf505a88307bd3d62b434c7d446d","tid":666354,"uid":145177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T21:45:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20d8971a80a9e6c50f31b32f70b33b1a98c19493","tid":666354,"uid":123456,"like":0,"d